{
  "stem": "8703.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community was about-- before the war, was about over 8,000, and gentiles, 2,000, about 10,000 altogether.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was really a Jewish, all Jewish businesses, you know, and-- mostly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, we had a very fine Jewish life that we didn't feel-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we felt like if we were home, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, we had, specially after World War I, the [NON-ENGLISH], instead going to yeshivas, they mostly were active people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, they formed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they joined Zionist or Socialist movements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they found their social life around these organizations, including me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was, even while I was in school, I joined all the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was very active [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] over that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were several.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had all of them in Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had Socialist Zionists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had a general Zionist, a religious Zionist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I belonged to the Betar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the nationalist movement, which they are-- they are-- they were interested to train the Jewish young people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They should be ready for Aliyah, to go to Israel and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] even fight for the creation of a Jewish state.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The majority of the young people in our city were the same opinion as I was, except socialists.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, it didn't bother me, as long as they were good Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were interested mostly of Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't see any future, those days, to stay in Poland, especially before-- between the two wars and in the 1930s, where anti-Semitism went rampant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why the Jewish young people didn't see any future staying in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The problem was that we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We tried illegal Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the English Mandate turned them down.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
